(1309, '随机图上顶点度数序列及树分图的分布 ', '贺国卿', '本文研究核心问题足利用概率方法分析随机图中顶点度数序列元素的分布怙况，为简化模型和得到般结果只对没有多条边和囵的简单无向图展开分析，这在网络通信厂rl属于常见模型之记（d）为随机图G∈G（n，p）中的度数序列，递减顺序排列为：d1≥d2≥…≥d，顶点之间连线的概率记为p=p（n），分析基于p=p（n）取值变化的顶点度数序列的概率分布怙况，进而确定最大度数元素的分布当p=p（n）取值固定时，分析基于冈贝尔分布的最大度数元素的极限分布随机图Gp中，用K=K（n）表示树分图的阶，T=T（Gp）表示K阶}对分图的数几，研究结果表明，p—p（n）取值变化的K阶孤立}对的期单值小同；并且，对固定的K，当p逐渐增JJ口到p～（k-1）／kn时，K阶孤树对的期望值逐渐增大，从而可以确定K阶孤市}对的最大期望数，本文讲究结果在网络通信中有潜存应用价值 ', '随机图； 顶点度数序列； 孤市树分图； 冈贝尔分布； ', 'CMFD', NULL, '1011263336.nh', 1, 'http://www.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?filename=1011263336.nh&amp;dbcode=CMFD&amp;dbname=CMFD2012', '0'),
(1310, 'The Diameter of a Scale-Free RandomGraph', ' B&amp;#233;la Bollob&amp;#225;s*, Oliver Riordan ', ' We consider a random graph process in which vertices areadded to the graph one at a time and joined to a fixed number m of earlier vertices, whereeach earlier vertex is chosen with probability proportional toits degree. This process was introduced by Barabási and Albert[3], as a simple model of the growth of real-world graphs suchas the world-wide web. Computer experiments presented byBarabási, Albert and Jeong [1,5] and heuristic arguments givenby Newman, Strogatz and Watts [23] suggest that after n steps the resulting graphshould have diameter approximately log n . We show that while this holds for m =1, for m ≥2 the diameter isasymptotically log n /loglog n . ', ' 05C80; ', 'SSJD_U', NULL, 'SSJD00002571116', 2, 'http://www.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?filename=SSJD00002571116&amp;dbcode=SSJD&amp;v=', '1011263336.nh'),
